Package: mcradds
Type: Package
Title: Processing and analyzing of In Vitro Diagnostic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kai", "Gu", , "gukai1212@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Maintainer: Kai Gu <gukai1212@163.com>
Description: A complement to 'mcr' package, adding methods and functions to 
    analyze the quantitative or qualitative performance for diagnostic tests. 
    And outliers detection, reader precision and reference range are discussed. 
    Most of the methods and algorithms refer to CLSI recommendations. In 
    additional, relevant plots are constructed by ggplot statement.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/kaigu1990/mcradds/, https://kaigu1990.github.io/mcradds/
BugReports: https://github.com/kaigu1990/mcradds/issues
